---
title: Work history - Apply for teacher training
scenario: |
  As part of an online service, you are providing information about previous jobs
  in the form of multiple job records. You are provided a page to check the records
  you've entered so far, add more or continue with the service.

  Things to try:

  1. You would like to change your answer for one of the questions for one of the records.
  2. You would like to delete a record
  3. You would like to add a new record

notes: The links to change your answers are not functional.
---

